| Function    | Explanation                                  |
| ----------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| Data hiding | Don’t expose sensitive fields                |
| Security    | Prevent mass assignment attacks              |
| Validation  | Apply `@NotNull`, `@Size` only to API fields |
| Performance | Smaller JSON payloads                        |
| Flexibility | Change DB without breaking API               |



| DTO                | Entity                |
| ------------------ | --------------------- |
| Used in API layer  | Used in DB layer      |
| No JPA annotations | Has `@Entity`, `@Id`  |
| API-specific       | DB-specific           |
| Safe to expose     | Should NOT be exposed |
